subject: HELLO
body:
HELLO
This is to inform you that you have been compensated by the United
States Government with a sum of 10 Million Dollars
Which has been received in my office yesterday I am sorry to inform
you lately because I was very busy
You are to choose how you want your fund to be received
(1) Bank to Bank wire Transfer
(2) Cash delivery
(3) Cheque

subject: Re: HELLO
body:
Dear Sir/Madam,

Thank you for your message. I would prefer to receive the funds via a bank-to-bank wire transfer. Could you please provide me with the necessary details to proceed with this?

Best wishes,
Norma
